item.title: CVE-2019-17332|2024-08-05T01:40:15.251Z -- tibco%20software%20inc. -- tibco%20ebx%20add-ons
item.description: The Digital Asset Manager Web Interface component of TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO EBX Add-ons contains a vulnerability that theoretically allows authenticated users to perform stored cross-site scripting (XSS) attacks. Affected releases are TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO EBX Add-ons: versions up to and including 3.20.13, versions 4.1.0, 4.2.0, 4.2.1, and 4.2.2.

item.title: CVE-2019-17331|2024-08-05T01:40:14.487Z -- tibco%20software%20inc. -- tibco%20ebx%20add-ons
item.description: The Data Exchange Web Interface component of TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO EBX Add-ons contains a vulnerability that theoretically allows authenticated users to perform stored cross-site scripting (XSS) attacks. Affected releases are TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO EBX Add-ons: versions up to and including 3.20.13, version 4.1.0.
